(19, 1, '2017-02-14 07:32:03', '2017-02-14 07:32:03', '\r\n\r\n<div class="top-header">\r\n	<div class="container">\r\n    	<div class="row" style="margin:0;">\r\n        	<div class="col-md-12 col-sm-12 col-xs-12">\r\n       <h2 class="blink text-center mdem22 smem20 xsem16 lh150 whitetext margin0 w600">\r\n            <strong>Review & My Mega Bonus Pack</strong></h2>\r\n			</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<section class="top">\r\n	<div class="container text-center">\r\n		<h2 class="thin italic">Professional Graphics in 3 Simple Steps</h2>\r\n		<h1 class="bold">Instantly Create Social Media & Advertising Graphics for ANY Social Media <br class="hidden-md-down hidden-xl-up">Platform <br class="hidden-md-up">in Seconds</h1>\r\n		<div class="row justify-content-center">\r\n			<div class="col viddiv">\r\n				<div class="embed-responsive embed-responsive-16by9">\r\n                  <iframe class="embed-responsive-item" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/Mj_33EuWPB8?rel=0&amp;showinfo=0&amp;controls=1&amp;autoplay=1" ></iframe>\r\n                </div>\r\n			</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n		<div class="col-md-8 col-md-offset-2 col-sm-offset-1 col-sm-10 col-xs-12 whitetext instant_button text-center margin_top2">\r\n			<a href="http://jvz1.com/c/10103/247083" style="padding:3% 0">\r\n			<div class="text-center w600 mdem22 smem20 xsem18">\r\n            <strong>Get Instant Access Here + My Mega Bonus Pack</strong></div>\r\n			</a></div>\r\n		<p>Supercharge your Social Media Message with Proven High Converting Graphics</p>\r\n	</div>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class="review" style="clear:both;">\r\n<div class="container">\r\n         	<div class="row">\r\n            	<div class="col-md-2 col-sm-3 col-xs-12"> \r\n                <img src="images/amitpic.jpg" class="center-block img-responsive" />               \r\n                </div>\r\n                <div class="col-md-10 col-sm-9 col-xs-12 margin_top3">\r\n                <p class="mdem16 smem15 xsem14 lh180 whitetext">\r\n     Hi! Dr. Amit Pareek here and here''s the review of "ReachMultiply" created by my team:		</p>\r\n                </div>\r\n                \r\n		<div class="col-md-12 col-sm-12 col-xs-12 margin_top4">\r\n        <p class="mdem16 smem15 xsem14 lh150 whitetext">\r\n \r\n\r\n\r\nThere are around 4-5 Social Networking Sites that are <br/>\r\nBest for Engaging Your Target Audience But<br/> \r\nwhen it comes to who is the MOST POPULAR Across The Globe then FACEBOOK IS THE KING!\r\n<br/><br/>\r\nAnd to Target Specific Audience through Facebook, we are required to \r\nPost on as many Walls, Pages, Groups etc. as possible to...  <br/>\r\n<br/><br/>\r\nGet Hordes of Traffic for Sales Pages of your Products, PLR Products, Websites, Affliate Stores, Blogs, etc.\r\n<br/><br/>\r\nAnd its a continuous process of Posting Content like Videos, Images, Text to <br/>\r\nimprove popularity of your Pages on Facebook so <br/>\r\nMax. people gets Engaged and give you Higher ROI.<br/><br/>\r\n\r\n\r\nBut, Do You know Why People Fail at FB Marketing? Because they are:<br/><br/>\r\n\r\nX Not Posting Content Regularly<br/>\r\nX Failing To Capitalize On Trends<br/>\r\nX Spending Too Much Time on Content\r\n<br/><br/>\r\nAs Creating and posting content on Facebook is very tiring, and<br/> \r\nmost content marketers give up too soon because<br/> \r\nthey just can’t make the effort consistently.\r\n<br/><br/>\r\nFacebook values consistency and if you don''t stay consistent,<br/> \r\nyou’re not going to climb up those engagement ranks. <br/>\r\n<br/><br/>\r\nAccording to a study, If you want success in fan page<br/> \r\nthen you have to post Minimum 2 Times Daily. <br/><br/>\r\n\r\nThat includes research, design and posting of 730 times a year<br/>\r\nand if you have multiple fanpages that’s a mammoth 3,650 posts a year!! \r\n<br/><br/>\r\nYou just can’t do this much work all alone <br/>\r\nand hiring someone to do the job is also not an option <br/>\r\nif you''re on a limited budget... <br/><br/>\r\n\r\nBut Now You have an Auotmated Option i.e. "ReachMultiply" <br/>\r\nand <br/>\r\nEvery Marketer including you Needs this<br/>\r\neven if you''re a Newbie or Expert:<br/>\r\n\r\n- Affiliate Marketer<br/>\r\n- Product Seller<br/>\r\n- Blogger,<br/>\r\n- A Niche Fan page owner or <br/>\r\n- An Offline Marketer<br/><br/>\r\n\r\n\r\nSo, Go for it if you want Maximum reach on your Facebook page effortlessly and <br/>\r\nBuild a long-term asset that you can drive sales from even if you’re not advertising!\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n \r\n\r\n \r\n</p>           \r\n</div>\r\n                  \r\n		</div>        \r\n	</div>                  \r\n</div>\r\n        \r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<section class="box">\r\n	<div class="container">\r\n		<h1 class="text-center bold">Introducing</h1>\r\n        <h2 class="text-center bold">Social Studio FX</h2>\r\n		<img src="images/box1.png">\r\n		<p class="text-center">The Ultimate Social Media Design Toolkit, Social Studio FX takes the\r\n		guesswork out of graphic design and walks you through the entire\r\n		process through three simple steps.</p>\r\n	</div>\r\n</section>\r\n<section class="step one">\r\n	<div class="container">\r\n		<div class="row align-items-center">\r\n			<div class="image col-md-6"><img src="images/1.png"></div>\r\n			<div class="col-md-6"><p class="bold">Select A Design <span class="bold nobreak">(Or Start From Scratch)</span></p>\r\n			<p>Browse over 200 visually stunning templates in 66 different sizes. The library features components in 23 niche categories, with a total of 13,200 different designs.</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n</section>\r\n<section class="step two">\r\n	<div class="container">\r\n		<div class="row align-items-center">\r\n			<div class="image col-md-6"><img src="images/2.png"></div>\r\n			<div class="col-md-6"><p class="bold">Customize Your Design</p>\r\n			<p>Point, click and customize your design effortlessly via a simple and user-friendly graphical interface. </p>\r\n			<p>Our 