(33, 1, '2017-02-15 09:25:34', '2017-02-15 09:25:34', '<div class="top-header">\n<div class="container">\n<div class="row" style="margin: 0;">\n<div class="col-md-12 col-sm-12 col-xs-12">\n<h2 class="blink text-center mdem22 smem20 xsem16 lh150 whitetext margin0 w600"><strong>Review &amp; My Mega Bonus Pack</strong></h2>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<section class="top">\n<div class="container text-center">\n<h2 class="thin italic">Professional Graphics in 3 Simple Steps</h2>\n<h1 class="bold">Instantly Create Social Media &amp; Advertising Graphics for ANY Social Media <br class="hidden-md-down hidden-xl-up" />Platform <br class="hidden-md-up" />in Seconds</h1>\n<div class="row justify-content-center">\n<div class="col viddiv">\n<div class="embed-responsive embed-responsive-16by9"><iframe class="embed-responsive-item" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/Mj_33EuWPB8?rel=0&amp;showinfo=0&amp;controls=1&amp;autoplay=1" width="300" height="150"></iframe></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="col-md-8 col-md-offset-2 col-sm-offset-1 col-sm-10 col-xs-12 whitetext instant_button text-center margin_top2">\n<div class="text-center w600 mdem22 smem20 xsem18"><strong>Get Instant Access Here + My Mega Bonus Pack</strong></div>\n</div>\nSupercharge your Social Media Message with Proven High Converting Graphics\n\n</div>\n</section>\n<div class="review" style="clear: both;">\n<div class="container">\n<div class="row">\n<div class="col-md-2 col-sm-3 col-xs-12">\n\n<img class="center-block img-responsive" src="http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/ashu.png" />\n\n</div>\n<div class="col-md-10 col-sm-9 col-xs-12 margin_top3">\n<p class="mdem16 smem15 xsem14 lh180 whitetext">Hi! Dr. Amit Pareek here and here''s the review of "ReachMultiply" created by my team:</p>\n\n</div>\n<div class="col-md-12 col-sm-12 col-xs-12 margin_top4">\n\nThere are around 4-5 Social Networking Sites that are\nBest for Engaging Your Target Audience But\nwhen it comes to who is the MOST POPULAR Across The Globe then FACEBOOK IS THE KING!\n\n\nAnd to Target Specific Audience through Facebook, we are required to\nPost on as many Walls, Pages, Groups etc. as possible to...\n\n\nGet Hordes of Traffic for Sales Pages of your Products, PLR Products, Websites, Affliate Stores, Blogs, etc.\n\n\nAnd its a continuous process of Posting Content like Videos, Images, Text to\nimprove popularity of your Pages on Facebook so\nMax. people gets Engaged and give you Higher ROI.\n\nBut, Do You know Why People Fail at FB Marketing? Because they are:\n\nX Not Posting Content Regularly\nX Failing To Capitalize On Trends\nX Spending Too Much Time on Content\n\n\nAs Creating and posting content on Facebook is very tiring, and\nmost content marketers give up too soon because\nthey just can’t make the effort consistently.\n\n\nFacebook values consistency and if you don''t stay consistent,\nyou’re not going to climb up those engagement ranks.\n\n\nAccording to a study, If you want success in fan page\nthen you have to post Minimum 2 Times Daily.\n\nThat includes research, design and posting of 730 times a year\nand if you have multiple fanpages that’s a mammoth 3,650 posts a year!!\n\n\nYou just can’t do this much work all alone\nand hiring someone to do the job is also not an option\nif you''re on a limited budget...\n\nBut Now You have an Auotmated Option i.e. "ReachMultiply"\nand\nEvery Marketer including you Needs this\neven if you''re a Newbie or Expert:\n\n- Affiliate Marketer\n- Product Seller\n- Blogger,\n- A Niche Fan page owner or\n- An Offline Marketer\n\nSo, Go for it if you want Maximum reach on your Facebook page effortlessly and\nBuild a long-term asset that you can drive sales from even if you’re not advertising!\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<section class="box">\n<div class="container">\n<h1 class="text-center bold">Introducing</h1>\n<h2 class="text-center bold">Social Studio FX</h2>\n<img src="images/box1.png" />\n<p class="text-center">The Ultimate Social Media Design Toolkit, Social Studio FX takes the\nguesswork out of graphic design and walks you through the entire\nprocess through three simple steps.</p>\n\n</div>\n</section><section class="step one">\n<div class="container">\n<div class="row align-items-center">\n<div class="image col-md-6"><img src="images/1.png" /></div>\n<div class="col-md-6">\n<p class="bold">Select A Design <span class="bold nobreak">(Or Start From Scratch)</span></p>\nBrowse over 200 visually stunning templates in 66 different sizes. The library features components in 23 niche categories, with a total of 13,200 different designs.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</section><section class="step two">\n<div class="container">\n<div class="row align-items-center">\n<div class="image col-md-6"><img src="images/2.png" /></div>\n<div class="col-md-6">\n<p class="bold">Customize Your Design</p>\nPoint, click and customize your design effortlessly via a simple and user-friendly graphical interface.\n\nOur powerful drag and drop technology allows for quick and precise editing!\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</section><section class="step three">\n<div class="container">\n<div class="row align-items-center">\n<div class="image col-md-6"><img src="images/3.png" /></div>\n<div class="col-md-6">\n<p class="bold">Download &amp; Publish</p>\nDownload quickly and seamlessly for use on your favorite social media or advertising platform. Available in PNG, JPEG, PDF or TIFF.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</section><section class="jimmy">\n<div class="container text-center">\n<h2 class="regular blurb"><span class="bold blue">Social Studio FX</span> is the <span class="bold orange">EXACT</span> tool we use in our business to generate sales and leads by simply leveraging the power of Social Media <span class="nobreak regular">&amp; Advertising.</span></h2>\n<h3 class="italic">Get your hands on <span class="nobreak">Social Studio FX today!</span></h3>\n<video autoplay="autoplay" loop="loop" width="300" height="150">\n<sourc